Sentencas: Preliminary progress is reported in this communication in building a planar anode-supported low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) stack based on gadolinia-doped ceria (GDC) electrolyte, i.e. fabrication and characterization of a 080 planar bilayer structure composed of GDC electrolyte film and Ni-GDC anode substrate.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of large-size electrolyte/anode bilayer structures for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell stack based on gadolinia-doped ceria electrolyte

Sentencas: The anode substrates were prepared from mixtures of NiO, GDC, and carbon black by die-pressing.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of large-size electrolyte/anode bilayer structures for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell stack based on gadolinia-doped ceria electrolyte

Sentencas: After pre-firing to remove the carbon black, the anode substrates were deposited with a GDC layer using a spray coating technique.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of large-size electrolyte/anode bilayer structures for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell stack based on gadolinia-doped ceria electrolyte

Sentencas: The green bilayers of anode substrate and electrolyte film were then co-sintered at 1500 degrees C for 3 h. Through proper control of the sintering process, bilayer structures with excellent flatness were achieved after co-sintering.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of large-size electrolyte/anode bilayer structures for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell stack based on gadolinia-doped ceria electrolyte

Sentencas: Scanning electron microscopy (SEM) observation indicated that the electrolyte film was about 22 mu m in thickness, highly dense, crack-free, and well-bonded to the anode substrate.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of large-size electrolyte/anode bilayer structures for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell stack based on gadolinia-doped ceria electrolyte

Sentencas: Small disks which were cut out from the 080 bilayer structure were electrochemically examined in a single button-cell mode incorporating a (LaSr)(CoFe)O-3-GDC composite cathode.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of large-size electrolyte/anode bilayer structures for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell stack based on gadolinia-doped ceria electrolyte

Sentencas: With humidified hydrogen as the fuel and air as the oxidant, the cell demonstrated an open-circuit voltage of 0.884 V and a maximum power density of 562 mW/cm(2) at 600 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of large-size electrolyte/anode bilayer structures for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell stack based on gadolinia-doped ceria electrolyte

Sentencas: The results imply that high-quality anode-supported electrolyte/anode bilayer structures were successfully fabricated.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of large-size electrolyte/anode bilayer structures for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell stack based on gadolinia-doped ceria electrolyte

Sentencas: Based on them, planar anode-supported SOFC stacks will be assembled in the future.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of large-size electrolyte/anode bilayer structures for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell stack based on gadolinia-doped ceria electrolyte
